- “¿Qué me recomiendas del menú?”
- “Es mi primera vez aquí”

Mango lessons introduced several useful real-world phrases involving:
- expensive locations
- dangerous areas
- modern vs cozy restaurants
- asking for help
- reservations under a person’s name

During practice rounds, the user demonstrated strong improvement in:
- movement/going phrases
- demonstrative adjective agreement
- conversational sentence construction
- confidence recalling phrases from memory

